Cloverdale Colts U13A1 Team Fundraiser

Support the Cloverdale Colts U13A1 team by contributing to our fundraiser. Your donations help us with travel, equipment, and tournament fees.

  1. Click on the Donate Now button.
  2. Create a Return-It account using the provided link. Your returns will be donated to the Cloverdale Colts by default.
  3. If you already have an account, click on Set Automatic Donation and search for Cloverdale Colts U13-A1 2025/2026.
  4. Bag your refundable containers into clear, 90L bags.
  5. Return all your empty beverage containers to a Return-It Express location.
  6. Enter your phone number (used to create your account) at the kiosk.
  7. Print labels, attach them to your bags, and the staff will count your containers. Funds will be deposited into your account.
